     "text": [
      "=== CLUSTERING: BASE vs SVD ===\n",
      "  Silhouette base (Ordinal, 16 vars) : 0.1473\n",
      "  Silhouette SVD  (OHE → 11 comps)   : 0.1467\n",
      "  Cambio                             : -0.0006\n",
      "\n",
      "=== CLASIFICACIÓN (Random Forest): BASE vs SVD ===\n",
