      "=== CLASIFICACIÓN (Random Forest): FE INICIAL (It.2) vs FE AMPLIADA + ORDINAL (It.3) ===\n",
      "  Accuracy : 0.9905 → 0.9905  (+0.0000)\n",
      "  F1 macro : 0.9904 → 0.9905  (+0.0001)\n",
